{"tid":1953840,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲連登仔真係好撚仆街","createTime":"2020-04-01T11:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T05:19:00.000Z","uid":137043,"like":34,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"105cd35c45ce8a8e8fb39520d704c97cef98ca3b","tid":1953840,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"見係女user，就算佢個post係講緊認真嘢<br />\n都會先入為主，屌咗人係雞先<br />\n話佢抵死、女人天生係咁低賤<br />\n<br />\n但如果係post性感相或者相關話題<br />\n就會有一大班狗公雞蟲仆住去阿諛奉承<br />\n不斷話有你做女朋友好撚幸福、好想照顧你<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢班仆街現實中係咪有精神分裂？<br />\n一時睇得自己好高，一時又成隻狗咁<br />\n係咪現實中比人恰得多、無成就感<br />\n先要上嚟一啲唔需要見樣嘅地方周圍發洩？<br />\n定係由細到大都無老豆老母教先咁？<br />\n呢班冚家鏟死咗都無人可憐<br />\n對任何嘢都無貢獻"},{"pid":"816a336820fed458372c1d6518757deb648cbec1","tid":1953840,"uid":134012,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"多得patreon"},{"pid":"6faea3776704860d5989eb6aef9b1a5ec9b5d5e3","tid":1953840,"uid":137043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"負評嘅講下有咩滿意"},{"pid":"10f37486b9bba37d0468a5d9b9b51ffcb5a84b6d","tid":1953840,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評嘅講下有咩唔滿意<br />\n我講錯啲咩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"31a4b15e3fb0f0bc111c6c09cc2a7c2c240789fe","tid":1953840,"uid":249015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:22:01.000Z","msg":"做咩事巴打激動到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上黎洗咩咁認真<br />\n好多人都係特登鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba5149e7d4ee35846b1e17dcd1919ba470314be","tid":1953840,"uid":333451,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"連登仔：<br />\n所有女人係雞<br />\n所有youtuber係乞衣<br />\n所有老師係教畜<br />\n所有基督徒係離地耶撚<br />\n<br />\n一出現就唔洗討論"},{"pid":"d723b58ae8662c7bc405800b37ff6c0cd2b69d56","tid":1953840,"uid":137043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a4b1